high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the bed.
Pick up alarm clock from the bed.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the dresser.
Place alarm clock on the dresser.
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the shelf.
Pick up alarm clock from the bed.
Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the dresser.
Place alarm clock on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collecting alarm clock from different places and arranging them on a dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight towards the end of the room and turn right side to enter into the bedroom and reach the bed
Take the alarm clock from the bed
Turn back and walk out of the bedroom. Then turn back and reach the dresser within the bedroom
Put the alarm clock on the dresser
Again enter into the bedroom and turn right to reach the shelf on the right side
Take the alarm clock from the shelf
Turn right and walk straight and turn left to walk out of the room. Then turn back and reach the dresser within the bedroom
Put the alarm clock on the dresser
anns.task_desc: Put the alarm clock on the dresser

high_descs: Turn around and go near the bed.
Take the alarm clock from the bed.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the alarm clock on the dresser.
Turn around and go near the shelf.
Take another alarm clock from the shelf.
Turn around and go near the dresser.
Put the alarm clock on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Collect the alarm clock and placed it on the dresser.
